{"tid":1088396,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警長張家輝涉盜竊 店員指閃縮","createTime":"2019-04-02T04:30:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T10:06:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"99a63b6ac4f3c63f46853a1085a54a35744f0655","tid":1088396,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T04:30:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190402/20647237\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190402%2F20647237&d=mFE05qKCD2WHpL72sA8m66ha%2BoeUeRXR1jLQ0PybHu0%3D&h=5cca0ce0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190402%2F20647237&h=9ad65f8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190402/20647237</a><br />\n<br />\n警長張家輝涉盜竊 店員指閃縮<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190402/large/02la6p6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190402%2Flarge%2F02la6p6.jpg&h=c722b856&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警長遭廉署拘捕被停職，疑情緒受困，約兩年後涉在深水埗某電子特賣場偷防滑貼及行李牌等總值32元的貨品，案件昨開審。店舖職員兼輔警供稱警長入店後「不時周圍望，行為上閃縮」，惹人懷疑，結果發現他只為部份貨品付款，其他贓物則放在手挽袋及褲袋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n案發後證實患重度抑鬱<br />\n<br />\n任輔警達26年的店員吳漢權昨供稱，事發於去年5月18日，他見被告張家輝（51歲，圖）離開店舖範圍時沒意圖付款，於是截停被告，被告表現得很驚，面色青白且說話「口窒窒」，及後稱：「唔好意思，我落去畀返」，其後發現小型多功能包、行李牌、LED燈等均沒付款。<br />\n<br />\n被告被裁表證成立，精神科專科醫生葉恩明供稱，被告妻子在2016年透露被告受廉署調查，情緒受困，「話先生唔開心，被冤枉，成日喊，唔知點做，憂慮冇咗份工」。被告在去年本案案發一周後向他求診，他發覺被告思想及行動緩慢，反應遲鈍，感到迷茫，斷定被告患上重度抑鬱，情緒低落、體重驟變、逃避社交。聆訊押後至本月25日，被告屆時會自辯。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC3886/18<br />\n<br />\n■記者陸羽平、戴國輝  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n菲女行山墮坡 消防營救15小時<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n任職北區醫院年做710宗剝牙手術 女牙醫患滑鼠手衞署賠2,000萬"},{"pid":"586d7d0bff750c41df5eeda363ba54393328aa71","tid":1088396,"uid":38472,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T04:34:29.000Z","msg":"警長帶頭為休班警先開紀錄。"},{"pid":"a0047be297845bfebd98a5ca8a31babe3b5fabca","tid":1088396,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T04:37:04.000Z","msg":"睇下佢哋有冇傾殺男人啫"},{"pid":"fb993d50064e004f15e640f2e0eb9eb0d1c6507f","tid":1088396,"uid":205138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T04:38:03.000Z","msg":"32蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff2cf385919530e5d74e2bd030dca0c4f9a9992","tid":1088396,"uid":178714,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T04:38:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/XaX-jzjEHaUIWSyz3K7-Lb_Turo9bvpBe6m4zUlb-2N9bplbF2Y-8UltuxIAZJjs4452dLqgr-CwRObN-ggKN1qoVLdhMsd3cXWN5tZWf56gGxan0U9zbG4f1Fd4cOZA3w\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh4.googleusercontent.com%2FXaX-jzjEHaUIWSyz3K7-Lb_Turo9bvpBe6m4zUlb-2N9bplbF2Y-8UltuxIAZJjs4452dLqgr-CwRObN-ggKN1qoVLdhMsd3cXWN5tZWf56gGxan0U9zbG4f1Fd4cOZA3w&h=5e3b18d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f69dffcfa59d9dbea0a8e252157ae7ef8fef276","tid":1088396,"uid":60524,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T04:39:41.000Z","msg":"情緒受困 死去一樓一放蛇唔比錢好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7666a8dff7235b61d482e28a465540acbe5cbb92","tid":1088396,"uid":95,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T04:54:29.000Z","msg":"自殺啦死差佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個月袋幾皮野返工蛇王叫雞唔俾錢仲話有情緒病，食撚屎啦！"},{"pid":"7eded081250512a44e91ddde5fda8f38a1ba744f","tid":1088396,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T04:56:06.000Z","msg":"最大犯罪組織幾時先會比人拉哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff9b636aea4f840779372f164c4c1ec5dff547c","tid":1088396,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T06:46:28.000Z","msg":"就算有得撈，五十五歲就要退休"},{"pid":"342